name: Tungevaag & Raaban
description: '''Tungevaag & Raaban''' was a dance music producer duo consisting of the Norwegian [[Martin Tungevaag]] from [[Stadlandet]] in Norway, and the Swedish [[Raaban|Robbin Söderlund]] (better known by his artistic name [[Raaban]]) from [[Borås]] in Sweden. Sharing a common interest for the [[Electronic dance music|EDM]] genre, they have both collaborated and separately produced music within the genre for many years. On December 9, 2019, the duo announced on [[Instagram]] that "creatively we will pursue different goals and paths".
